{"title":"vscode常用快捷键","date":"2020-02-07T10:05:50.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年2月7日","L":"2020/02/07","MM-DD":"02-07"},"link":"2020/02/07/2020-02-07","tags":["VSCode"],"updated":"2024-01-24T01:26:39.000Z","content":"<h2 id=\"简介\">简介<a title=\"#简介\" href=\"#简介\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>vscode作为一个前端开发工具来说是非常方便的。作为巨硬的开源代码编辑器，不仅<br>\n有着众多的用户，还有着活跃的社区，这给vscode带来了数不胜数的插件。使用<br>\n插件辅助开发的同时，不要忘了vscode本身也是一款拥有许多快捷键的高效工具。<br>\n我把常用的快捷键概括了一下，记下的同时也方便自己以后查阅。窗口相关的大部分<br>\n快捷键与chrome一样，vscode平常使用习惯了，chrome的使用也变得更高效了🙃</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"文件相关\">文件相关<a title=\"#文件相关\" href=\"#文件相关\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>打开文件</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Cmd+O</span><br><span class=\"line\">Ctrl+O</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>快速打开文件</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Cmd+P</span><br><span class=\"line\">Ctrl+P</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>新建文件</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Cmd+N</span><br><span class=\"line\">Ctrl+N</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"窗口界面相关\">窗口界面相关<a title=\"#窗口界面相关\" href=\"#窗口界面相关\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>关闭窗口</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Cmd+W </span><br><span class=\"line\">Ctrl+W</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>撤销窗口关闭</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Shift+Cmd+T</span><br><span class=\"line\">Shift+Ctrl+T</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>终端开关</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Ctrl+`</span><br><span class=\"line\">Ctrl+`</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>侧边栏开关</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Cmd+B </span><br><span class=\"line\">Ctrl+B</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>面板开关</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Shift+Cmd+P</span><br><span class=\"line\">Shift+Ctrl+P</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"代码编辑相关\">代码编辑相关<a title=\"#代码编辑相关\" href=\"#代码编辑相关\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>选中单词</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Cmd+D</span><br><span class=\"line\">Ctrl+D</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>向下/上复制一行</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Shift+Option+Up</span><br><span class=\"line\">Shift+Option+Down</span><br><span class=\"line\">Shift+Alt+Up</span><br><span class=\"line\">Shift+Alt+Down</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>删除整行</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ShiftCmd+K</span><br><span class=\"line\">Shift+Ctrl+K</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>行尾/行首移动</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Cmd+Right</span><br><span class=\"line\">Cmd+Left</span><br><span class=\"line\">Ctrl+Right</span><br><span class=\"line\">Ctrl+Left</span><br><span class=\"line\">home</span><br><span class=\"line\">end</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>以空格为分隔的光标移动</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Option+Right</span><br><span class=\"line\">Option+Left</span><br><span class=\"line\">Alt+Right</span><br><span class=\"line\">Alt+Left</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>在下一行插入</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Cmd+Enter </span><br><span class=\"line\">Ctrl+Enter</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>连续选中单词</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Shift+Option+left/right</span><br><span class=\"line\">Shift+Alt+left/right</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"消费跟踪工具","link":"2020/03/04/2020-03-04"},"next":{"title":"chrome倍速播放插件","link":"2020/01/06/2020-01-06"},"plink":"https://pi-char.github.io/2020/02/07/2020-02-07/","toc":[{"id":"简介","title":"简介","index":"1"},{"id":"文件相关","title":"文件相关","index":"2"},{"id":"窗口界面相关","title":"窗口界面相关","index":"3"},{"id":"代码编辑相关","title":"代码编辑相关","index":"4"}],"reading_time":"393 字约 3 分钟"}